Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Christa McAuliffe and the Challenger disaster, 1986
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydpjw
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 31 Jan 1986
Alistair Cooke reflects on the life and death of Christa McAuliffe, the first civilian astronaut who was killed in the space shuttle Challenger disaster on 28th January 1986.